trans-unit.source: Contains filter criteria for data extracted from a workflow instance in a <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingQueryOptions"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Contém os critérios de filtro para dados extraídos a partir de uma instância de fluxo de trabalho num <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingQueryOptions"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] A TrackingDataItemValue specifies the value of a piece of data extracted from a workflow.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]Um TrackingDataItemValue Especifica o valor de um conjunto de dados extraídos de um fluxo de trabalho.

trans-unit.source: It is used to constrain the set of <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance> objects returned by <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingQuery.GetWorkflows%2A?displayProperty=fullName> in a query of the tracking data base used by a <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingService>.
trans-unit.target: É utilizado para restringir o conjunto de <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance>objetos devolvido <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingQuery.GetWorkflows%2A?displayProperty=fullName>numa consulta de base de dados de controlo utilizada por um <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingService>.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingService> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingQuery.GetWorkflows%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance>

trans-unit.source: You can add TrackingDataItemValue objects to <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingQueryOptions.TrackingDataItems%2A?displayProperty=fullName> to specify that the set of <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance> objects returned by <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingQuery.GetWorkflows%2A?displayProperty=fullName> be constrained to those possessing the specified set of extracted data.
trans-unit.target: Pode adicionar objetos TrackingDataItemValue <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingQueryOptions.TrackingDataItems%2A?displayProperty=fullName>para especificar que o conjunto de <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance>objectos devolvidos pelo <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingQuery.GetWorkflows%2A?displayProperty=fullName>estar limitado às possessing o conjunto de dados extraídos especificados.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingQuery.GetWorkflows%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingQueryOptions.TrackingDataItems%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância do <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue"> </xref> classe.

trans-unit.source: The default constructor initializes <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue.DataValue%2A>, <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue.FieldName%2A>, and <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue.QualifiedName%2A> to a null reference (`Nothing` in Visual Basic).
trans-unit.target: O construtor predefinido inicializa <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue.DataValue%2A>, <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue.FieldName%2A>, e <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue.QualifiedName%2A>para uma referência nula (`Nothing` no Visual Basic).</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue.QualifiedName%2A> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue.FieldName%2A> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue.DataValue%2A>

trans-unit.source: You must set all of these properties in order to configure the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue>.
trans-unit.target: Tem de definir todas estas propriedades para configurar o <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue>.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue"></xref> class by using the specified qualified name of an activity, data field name, and <xref uid="langword_csharp_string" name="string" href=""></xref> representation of a data value.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância do <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue"> </xref> classe utilizando o nome qualificado especificado de uma atividade, o nome do campo de dados, e <xref uid="langword_csharp_string" name="string" href=""> </xref> representação de um valor de dados.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue.QualifiedName%2A>, <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue.FieldName%2A>, and <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue.DataValue%2A> properties are set according to the values specified by the equivalent parameters to the constructor.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue.QualifiedName%2A>, <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue.FieldName%2A>, e <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue.DataValue%2A>propriedades forem definidas, de acordo com os valores especificados pelos parâmetros equivalentes a este construtor.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue.DataValue%2A> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue.FieldName%2A> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue.QualifiedName%2A>

trans-unit.target: O nome qualificado da atividade a partir da qual os dados foi extraídos.

trans-unit.target: O nome do membro a partir da qual os dados foi extraídos.

trans-unit.target: Obtém ou define um <xref uid="langword_csharp_string" name="string" href=""> </xref> representação do valor dos dados extraídos.

trans-unit.source: DataValue can be a null reference (`Nothing`).

trans-unit.target: A <xref uid="langword_csharp_string" name="string" href=""> </xref> representação do valor dos dados extraídos.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the name of the activity member from which the data was extracted.
trans-unit.target: Obtém ou define o nome do membro atividade a partir da qual os dados foi extraídos.

trans-unit.source: FieldName corresponds to the name specified in a <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItem.FieldName%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.
trans-unit.target: FieldName corresponde ao nome especificado no <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItem.FieldName%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItem.FieldName%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: FieldName can, therefore, be set to specify an activity field or property; a member of an activity field or property; or a single element of an activity field or property (or a member of either) that implements the <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerable> interface.
trans-unit.target: FieldName pode, por conseguinte, ser definido para especificar um campo de atividade ou propriedade; um membro de um campo de atividade ou propriedade; ou um único elemento de propriedade ou um campo de atividade (ou um membro do), que implementa o <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerable>interface.</xref:System.Collections.IEnumerable>

trans-unit.source: For more information see <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItem.FieldName%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingExtract.Member%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract.Member%2A?displayProperty=fullName> or <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowDataTrackingExtract.Member%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.
trans-unit.target: Para obter mais informações consulte <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItem.FieldName%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingExtract.Member%2A?displayProperty=fullName> <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract.Member%2A?displayProperty=fullName>ou <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowDataTrackingExtract.Member%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowDataTrackingExtract.Member%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract.Member%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingExtract.Member%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItem.FieldName%2A?displayProperty=fullName>
